title: Ground News - Coroners identify 47-year-old found shot to death inside car in California neighborhood
text:
Summary by Ground News Louisville Metro Police Department responded to the 1500 block of Prentice Street on Tuesday around 5:23 p.m. When officers arrived, they found 47-year-old Roderick McKisick suffering from a gunshot wound inside a car. No arrests have been made at this time. Share menu More
